      • coalesce

        public static DGAConfiguration coalesce(DGAConfiguration... configurationsInOrder)
        This method returns a new DGAConfiguration object containing the resulting coalescing activity of all provided DGAConfigurations The order of the configurations is important -- the configuration with the lowest priority will be added first, then the second, and so on. This means the last configuration passed in will trump all previous configurations if a collision in property name will occur.
        Parameters:
        configurationsInOrder - The order to apply configurations in the resulting
        Returns:
